\section*{1. Definition}
- Data security is the protection of computer hardware, computer software (programs) and data in the computer and communication system against unauthorized modification, destruction, disclosure or transfer whether accidental or intentional

\section*{2. Data control}
- Data control is the measures taken to enforce the security of the programs and data
- In order to protect against data lose, control measures need to be put in place. These controls may be just procedures, software or hardware
